      "instruction": "<p>Top the chicken<strong> </strong>evenly with your <strong>‘Nduja </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!)</p><p>Put the tray[s] in the oven for 15-20 min or until the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!) – this is your <strong>‘Nduja-topped chicken</strong></p><p>Meanwhile, wash your <strong>salad</strong>, then<strong> </strong>pat dry with kitchen paper</p>",
