    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel and finely chop your <strong>shallot[s],<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span></strong>then add to a large bowl with your <strong>cider vinegar</strong>,<strong> </strong>1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil</strong> and <strong>Dijon mustard</strong></p><p>Add most of the <strong>salad </strong>to the bowl (you'll use the rest later!), then season with a grind of <strong>pepper </strong>and give everything a good mix up</p>",
