    {
      "instruction": "<p>Cut your <strong>cucumber</strong> into quarters lengthways, then slice finely</p><p>Cut 2 slices per person from your<strong> tomato[es]</strong> and set aside for later, then finely dice the rest</p><p>Add the<strong> sliced cucumber</strong> and <strong>diced tomato</strong> (keeping the sliced tomato aside for later!) to the salad bowl and give everything a good mix up – this is your<strong> tomato & cucumber salad</strong></p>",
