      "instruction": "<p>Once the fries are done, remove them from the oven, push to one side and top with your<strong> grated Italian hard cheese</strong></p><p>Cut your <strong>ciabatta[s]</strong> in half and add to the other side of the tray[s]</p><p>Return the tray[s] to the oven for 2-3 min until the cheese has melted and the ciabatta is warmed through</p>",
