      "instruction": "<p>Fill the <strong>warmed</strong> <strong>ciabatta </strong>with a dollop of <strong>black pepper mayo</strong>, the <strong>roasted pepper</strong>,<strong> ‘Nduja-topped chicken</strong>, <strong>reserved salad </strong>and <strong>sliced tomato </strong>– this is your <strong>chicken, ‘Nduja & roasted pepper sandwich</strong></p><p>Serve with the <strong>tomato & cucumber salad</strong>, <strong>cheesy fries</strong> and any <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>black pepper mayo </strong>to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
